=== Commands Listing ===

Drop down menu available via Tools -> Packages -> CTags.

|=Command                        |=Key Binding              |
| rebuildCTags                   | ctrl+alt+shift+t         |
| navigateToDefinition           | ctrl+rightbracket        |
| jumpBack                       | ctrl+leftbracket         |
| jumpBack toLastModification    | ctrl+shift+leftbracket   |
| showSymbols                    | alt+s                    |
| showSymbols multi              | alt+shift+s              |